Process called "create_capability_set" that takes allowed as List[Capability] and denied as List[Capability] returns CapabilitySet:
    Let effective_caps be list containing Note: Start with a minimal set and add allowed capabilities
    For each capability in allowed:
    If not Collections.List.contains with lst as denied and item as capability:
    Add capability to effective_caps Return CapabilitySet with:
    effective as effective_caps
    permitted as effective_caps
    inheritable as list containing
    bounding as effective_caps
    ambient as list containing

