Process called "calculate_uptime" that takes sandbox as Sandbox returns Integer:
    Let current_time be DateTime.now_milliseconds()
    Let creation_time be DateTime.to_milliseconds with datetime as sandbox.created_at
    Return current_time - creation_time divided by 1000

